[
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"0227\" class=\"\">Then</st> <st data-num=\"03091\" class=\"\">Joshua</st> <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">summoned</st> the <st data-num=\"07206\" class=\"\">Reubenites</st>, the <st data-num=\"01425\" class=\"\">Gadites</st>, and the <st data-num=\"02677\" class=\"\">half</st>-<st data-num=\"04294\" class=\"\">tribe</st> of <st data-num=\"04519\" class=\"\">Manasseh</st> ",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "and <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">told</st> them: \u201c<st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">You</st> have <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">carried out</st> <st data-num=\"03605 0834\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">instructions</st> of <st data-num=\"04872\" class=\"\">Moses</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st>, and you have <st data-num=\"08085 06963\">obeyed</st> <st data-num=\"03605 0834\">all</st> I have <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">told</st> you.<n id=\"1\" />",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "You have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">abandoned</st> your <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">fellow Israelites</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">entire</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">right up to</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> very <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>. You have <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">completed</st> the <st data-num=\"04931\" class=\"\">task</st> <st data-num=\"04687\" class=\"\">given</st> you by the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> ",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">Now</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> has <st data-num=\"05117\" class=\"\">made</st> your <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">fellow Israelites</st> <st data-num=\"05117\" class=\"\">secure</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> just <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">as</st> he <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">promised</st> them. So <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st> you may <st data-num=\"06437\" class=\"\">turn around</st> and <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">go</st> to your <st data-num=\"0168\" class=\"\">homes</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">in</st> your <st data-num=\"0272\" class=\"\">own</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"04872\" class=\"\">Moses</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">assigned</st> to you <st data-num=\"05676\" class=\"\">east</st> of the <st data-num=\"03383\" class=\"\">Jordan</st>. ",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"07535\" class=\"\">But</st> <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">carefully</st> <st data-num=\"08104 06213\">obey</st> the <st data-num=\"04687\" class=\"\">commands</st> and <st data-num=\"08451 0834\">instructions</st> <st data-num=\"04872\" class=\"\">Moses</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servant</st> <st data-num=\"06680\" class=\"\">gave</st> you. <st data-num=\"0157\" class=\"\">Love</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>, <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">follow</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> his <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">instructions</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">obey</st><n id=\"3\" /> his <st data-num=\"04687\" class=\"\">commands</st>, <st data-num=\"01692\" class=\"\">be loyal</st> to him,<n id=\"4\" /> and <st data-num=\"05647\" class=\"\">serve</st> him with <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> your <st data-num=\"03824\" class=\"\">heart</st> and <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">being</st>!\u201d<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03091\" class=\"\">Joshua</st> <st data-num=\"01288\" class=\"\">rewarded</st><n id=\"1\" /> them and <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> them <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">on</st> their <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">way</st>; they <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">returned</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> their <st data-num=\"0168\" class=\"\">homes</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "(Now to one <st data-num=\"02677\" class=\"\">half</st>-<st data-num=\"07626\" class=\"\">tribe</st> of <st data-num=\"04519\" class=\"\">Manasseh</st>, <st data-num=\"04872\" class=\"\">Moses</st> had <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">assigned</st> land in <st data-num=\"01316\" class=\"\">Bashan</st>; and to the other <st data-num=\"02677\" class=\"\">half</st> <st data-num=\"03091\" class=\"\">Joshua</st> had <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">assigned</st> land on the <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">west</st> <st data-num=\"05676\" class=\"\">side</st> of the <st data-num=\"03383\" class=\"\">Jordan</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> their <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">fellow Israelites</st>.) <st data-num=\"01571 03588\">When</st> <st data-num=\"03091\" class=\"\">Joshua</st> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> them <st data-num=\"0413 0168\">home</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> he <st data-num=\"01288\" class=\"\">rewarded</st><n id=\"2\" /> them, ",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0559 0413 0559\">saying</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">Take</st> <st data-num=\"0413 0168\">home</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"05233\" class=\"\">wealth</st>, <st data-num=\"07227 03966\">a lot of</st> <st data-num=\"04735\" class=\"\">cattle</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st>, <st data-num=\"02091\" class=\"\">gold</st>, <st data-num=\"05178\" class=\"\">bronze</st>, <st data-num=\"01270\" class=\"\">iron</st>, and <st data-num=\"07235 03966\">a lot of</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"08008\" class=\"\">clothing</st>. <st data-num=\"02505\" class=\"\">Divide up</st> the <st data-num=\"07998\" class=\"\">goods</st> captured from your <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> your <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">brothers</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "So the <st data-num=\"01121 07205\">Reubenites</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121 01410\">Gadites</st>, and the <st data-num=\"02677\" class=\"\">half</st>-<st data-num=\"07626\" class=\"\">tribe</st> of <st data-num=\"04519\" class=\"\">Manasseh</st> <st data-num=\"07725 01980 0854\">left</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 03478\">Israelites</st> in <st data-num=\"07887 0834\">Shiloh</st> in the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of <st data-num=\"03667\" class=\"\">Canaan</st> and <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">headed</st> home <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> their <st data-num=\"0272\" class=\"\">own</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> <st data-num=\"0413 0776\">in</st> <st data-num=\"01568\" class=\"\">Gilead</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">which</st> they <st data-num=\"0270\" class=\"\">acquired</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">by</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">command</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">through</st> <st data-num=\"04872\" class=\"\">Moses</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <st data-num=\"01121 07205\">Reubenites</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121 01410\">Gadites</st>, and the <st data-num=\"02677\" class=\"\">half</st>-<st data-num=\"07626\" class=\"\">tribe</st> of <st data-num=\"04519\" class=\"\">Manasseh</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"01552\" class=\"\">Geliloth</st> near the <st data-num=\"03383\" class=\"\">Jordan</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">in</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of <st data-num=\"03667\" class=\"\">Canaan</st> and <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">built</st> <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st>, <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">near</st> the <st data-num=\"03383\" class=\"\">Jordan</st>, an <st data-num=\"01419 04758\">impressive</st> <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"01121 03478\">Israelites</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">received</st> this <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">report</st>:<n id=\"1\" /> \u201c<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121 07205\">Reubenites</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121 01410\">Gadites</st>, and the <st data-num=\"02677\" class=\"\">half</st>-<st data-num=\"07626\" class=\"\">tribe</st> of <st data-num=\"04519\" class=\"\">Manasseh</st> have <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">built</st> an <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">at</st> the <st data-num=\"04136\" class=\"\">entrance to</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of <st data-num=\"03667\" class=\"\">Canaan</st>, <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">at</st> <st data-num=\"01552\" class=\"\">Geliloth</st> near the <st data-num=\"03383\" class=\"\">Jordan</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 03478\">Israelite</st> <st data-num=\"05676\" class=\"\">side</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "When the <st data-num=\"01121 03478\">Israelites</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> this, the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">entire</st> <st data-num=\"01121 03478\">Israelite</st> <st data-num=\"05712\" class=\"\">community</st> <st data-num=\"06950\" class=\"\">assembled</st> at <st data-num=\"07887\" class=\"\">Shiloh</st> to <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">launch</st> an <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">attack</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> them.<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <st data-num=\"01121 03478\">Israelites</st> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> <st data-num=\"06372\" class=\"\">Phinehas</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"0499\" class=\"\">Eleazar</st>, the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priest</st>, <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of <st data-num=\"01568\" class=\"\">Gilead</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 07205\">Reubenites</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121 01410\">Gadites</st>, and the <st data-num=\"02677\" class=\"\">half</st>-<st data-num=\"07626\" class=\"\">tribe</st> of <st data-num=\"04519\" class=\"\">Manasseh</st>. ",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "He was <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">accompanied</st> by <st data-num=\"06235\" class=\"\">10</st> <st data-num=\"05387\" class=\"\">leaders</st>, <st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">one</st> from <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">each</st> of the <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israelite</st> <st data-num=\"04294\" class=\"\">tribes</st>, <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">each one</st> a <st data-num=\"01004 01\">family</st> <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">leader</st> among the <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israelite</st> <st data-num=\"0505\" class=\"\">clans</st>.<n id=\"1\" />",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "They <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">went</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of <st data-num=\"01568\" class=\"\">Gilead</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 07205\">Reubenites</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121 01410\">Gadites</st>, and the <st data-num=\"02677\" class=\"\">half</st>-<st data-num=\"07626\" class=\"\">tribe</st> of <st data-num=\"04519\" class=\"\">Manasseh</st>, and <st data-num=\"01696 0559\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">to</st> them: ",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "\u201cThe <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">entire</st> <st data-num=\"05712\" class=\"\">community</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">says</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Why</st> have you <st data-num=\"04603 02088 0834 04603\">disobeyed</st> the <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> by <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">turning back</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">today</st> from <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">following</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>? You <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">built</st> an <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> for yourselves and have <st data-num=\"04775\" class=\"\">rebelled</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">today</st> against the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">sin</st> we committed at <st data-num=\"06465\" class=\"\">Peor</st> was <st data-num=\"04592\" class=\"\">bad enough</st>. <st data-num=\"0834 05704\">To</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> very <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> we have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"02891 04480\">purified</st> ourselves; it even <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">brought</st> a <st data-num=\"05063\" class=\"\">plague</st> on the <st data-num=\"05712\" class=\"\">community</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "Now <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">today</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> dare to <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">turn back</st><n id=\"1\" /> from <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">following</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>! <st data-num=\"01961 0859\">You</st> are <st data-num=\"04775\" class=\"\">rebelling</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">today</st> against the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>; <st data-num=\"04279\" class=\"\">tomorrow</st> he may <st data-num=\"07107\" class=\"\">break out in anger</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">against</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">entire</st> <st data-num=\"05712\" class=\"\">community</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. ",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0389\" class=\"\">But</st> <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">if</st> your <st data-num=\"0272\" class=\"\">own</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st><n id=\"1\" /> is <st data-num=\"02931\" class=\"\">impure</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">cross over</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"0272\" class=\"\">own</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"0834 08033\">where</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"04908 03068\">Lord</st></span> himself <st data-num=\"07931\" class=\"\">lives</st>,<n id=\"4\" /> and <st data-num=\"0270\" class=\"\">settle down</st> <st data-num=\"08432\" class=\"\">among</st> us.<n id=\"5\" /> But <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"04775\" class=\"\">rebel</st> against the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">or</st> us<n id=\"6\" /> by <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">building</st> for yourselves an <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> <st data-num=\"01107\" class=\"\">other</st> than the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> our <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>. ",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "When <st data-num=\"05912\" class=\"\">Achan</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"02226\" class=\"\">Zerah</st> <st data-num=\"04603 04604\">disobeyed the command</st> about the city\u2019s <st data-num=\"02764\" class=\"\">riches</st>, the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">entire</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israelite</st> <st data-num=\"05712\" class=\"\">community</st> <st data-num=\"03808 01961\">was</st> <st data-num=\"05921 07110\">judged</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> though <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">only</st> <st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">one</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> had sinned. He most <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">certainly</st> <st data-num=\"01478\" class=\"\">died</st> for his <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">sin</st>!\u2019\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <st data-num=\"01121 07205\">Reubenites</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121 01410\">Gadites</st>, and the <st data-num=\"02677\" class=\"\">half</st>-<st data-num=\"07626\" class=\"\">tribe</st> of <st data-num=\"04519\" class=\"\">Manasseh</st> <st data-num=\"06030 01696 0854\">answered</st> the <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">leaders</st><n id=\"1\" /> of the <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israelite</st> <st data-num=\"0505\" class=\"\">clans</st>:",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "\u201c<st data-num=\"0410\" class=\"\">El</st>, <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>!<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0410\" class=\"\">El</st>, <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>! <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">He</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">knows</st> the truth!<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03478 01931\">Israel</st> must also <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st>! <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">If</st> we have <st data-num=\"04777\" class=\"\">rebelled</st> <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"04604\" class=\"\">disobeyed</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"03467\" class=\"\">spare</st> us<n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"03117 02088\">today</st>! ",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "If we have <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">built</st><n id=\"1\" /> an <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> for ourselves to <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">turn back</st> from <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">following</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> by <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">making</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt sacrifices</st> and <st data-num=\"04503\" class=\"\">grain offerings</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> it, <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">or</st> by <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">offering</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"02077\" class=\"\">tokens</st> of <st data-num=\"08002\" class=\"\">peace</st><n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> it, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">himself</st> will <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">punish</st> us.<n id=\"5\" />",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0518 03808\">We swear</st> we have <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">done</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"01674 01697\">because we were worried</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">that</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"04279\" class=\"\">in the future</st> your <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">descendants</st> would <st data-num=\"0559 0559\">say</st> to our <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">descendants</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What</st> relationship do you have with the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>?<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">made</st> the <st data-num=\"03383\" class=\"\">Jordan</st> a <st data-num=\"01366\" class=\"\">boundary</st> <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">between</st> us <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">and</st> you <st data-num=\"01121 07205\">Reubenites</st> and <st data-num=\"01121 01410\">Gadites</st>. You have <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"02506\" class=\"\">right to worship</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.\u2019<n id=\"1\" /> In this way your <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">descendants</st> might cause our <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">descendants</st> to <st data-num=\"07673 01115\">stop</st> <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">obeying</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. ",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "So we <st data-num=\"0559 06213 04994\">decided</st> to <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">build</st> this <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st>, <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> for <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt offerings</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"02077\" class=\"\">sacrifices</st>, ",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">but</st> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">as</st> a <st data-num=\"05707\" class=\"\">reminder</st> <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">to</st> us <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">and</st> you<n id=\"1\" /> and our <st data-num=\"01755\" class=\"\">descendants</st> who <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">follow</st> us, that we will <st data-num=\"05647 05656\">honor</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> in his very <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">presence</st><n id=\"2\" /> with <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt offerings</st>, <st data-num=\"02077\" class=\"\">sacrifices</st>, and <st data-num=\"08002\" class=\"\">tokens of peace</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> Then <st data-num=\"04279\" class=\"\">in the future</st> your <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">descendants</st> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> be able to <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st> to our <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">descendants</st>, \u2018You have <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"02506\" class=\"\">right to worship</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.\u2019<n id=\"4\" /> ",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "We <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"01961 03588\">If</st> <st data-num=\"04279\" class=\"\">in the future</st> they <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st> such a thing<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> us or <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> our <st data-num=\"01755\" class=\"\">descendants</st>, we will <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">reply</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">See</st> the <st data-num=\"08403\" class=\"\">model</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> our <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">ancestors</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">made</st>, <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> for <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt offerings</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"02077\" class=\"\">sacrifices</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">but</st> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">as</st> a <st data-num=\"05707\" class=\"\">reminder</st> <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">to</st> us <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">and</st> you.\u201d\u2019<n id=\"3\" />",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"02486\" class=\"\">Far be it</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> us to <st data-num=\"04775\" class=\"\">rebel</st> against the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> by <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">turning back</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">today</st> from following <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">after</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> by <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">building</st> an <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> for <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt offerings</st>, <st data-num=\"04503\" class=\"\">sacrifices</st>, and <st data-num=\"02077\" class=\"\">tokens of peace</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0905\" class=\"\">aside from</st> the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> our <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">located</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">in front of</st> his <st data-num=\"04908\" class=\"\">dwelling place</st>!\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "29"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">When <st data-num=\"06372\" class=\"\">Phinehas</st> the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priest</st> and the <st data-num=\"05712\" class=\"\">community</st> <st data-num=\"05387\" class=\"\">leaders</st> and <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"0505\" class=\"\">clan</st> <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">leaders</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">accompanied</st> him <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> the <st data-num=\"01697 0834 01696\">defense of</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 07205\">Reubenites</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121 01410\">Gadites</st>, and the <st data-num=\"01121 04519\">Manassehites</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">they</st> <st data-num=\"03190\" class=\"\">were satisfied</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "30"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"06372\" class=\"\">Phinehas</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"0499\" class=\"\">Eleazar</st>, the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priest</st>, <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 07205\">Reubenites</st>, the <st data-num=\"01121 01410\">Gadites</st>, and the <st data-num=\"01121 04519\">Manassehites</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201c<st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">Today</st> we <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> is <st data-num=\"08432\" class=\"\">among</st> us <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">because</st> you have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"04603\" class=\"\">disobeyed</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"04604 02088\">in this</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0227\" class=\"\">Now</st><n id=\"3\" /> you have <st data-num=\"05337\" class=\"\">rescued</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 03478\">Israelites</st> from the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">judgment</st>.\u201d<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "31"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"06372\" class=\"\">Phinehas</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"0499\" class=\"\">Eleazar</st>, the <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priest</st>, and the <st data-num=\"05387\" class=\"\">leaders</st> <st data-num=\"07725 0954\">left</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 07205\">Reubenites</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"01121 01410\">Gadites</st> in the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of <st data-num=\"01568\" class=\"\">Gilead</st> and <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">reported</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">back</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 03478\">Israelites</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">in</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of <st data-num=\"03667\" class=\"\">Canaan</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "32"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"01121 03478\">Israelites</st> <st data-num=\"03190 05869\">were satisfied with</st> their <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">report</st> and <st data-num=\"01288\" class=\"\">gave thanks to</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> They <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">nothing</st> more about <st data-num=\"05927 05921\">launching</st> an <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">attack</st> to <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">destroy</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> in <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">which</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 07205\">Reubenites</st> and <st data-num=\"01121 01410\">Gadites</st> <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">lived</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "33"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Joshua",
    "chapter": "22",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"01121 07205\">Reubenites</st> and <st data-num=\"01121 01410\">Gadites</st> <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">named</st> the <st data-num=\"04196\" class=\"\">altar</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Surely</st> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">it</st> is a <st data-num=\"05707\" class=\"\">Reminder</st> <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">to</st> us<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> is <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "34"
  }
]